Inputs:
  user identification (eg. student ID, number plate)
  entry sensor signal (car at gate)
  exist sensor signal (car leaving)

Outputs:
  barrier control (open/close)
  display value (number of parking spots available)
  alert signal (light, buzzer, message when car park is full and someones tries to enter)

Constants:
  Max_capacity (200 total car park sports)

Variables:
  CarParked (the number of cars currently inside the car park)
  availableSpots ( calculated as CarParked - availableSpots)
  isRegistered (true/false for the user at the gate)
  isFull (true if CarParked == Max_capacity)
